<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.194107>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 2. Dendrozetes jordani n. sp., adult female. 1, Dorsal aspect; 2, Ventral aspect. Legs removed. Scale bars = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/194107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.194108>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 A – D. Dendrozetes jordani n. sp., legs of adult female, legs I and II adaxial aspect, legs III and IV abaxial aspect, all legs trochanters removed: 9 A, leg I; 9 B, leg II; 9 C, leg III; 9 D, leg IV. Scale bar = 100 um." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/194108/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.194109>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Average abundance (+ SE) (# individuals per 100 gm dry weight of substrate) of Dendrozetes jordani n. sp. adults and immatures collected from branch tip and foliose lichens in Abies amabilis and Tsuga heterophylla trees over three seasons of 1996; from the Montane Alternative Silvicultural Systems study area, Vancouver Island." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/194109/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

